00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:33,800
It's been a long time.

569
00:34:33,800 --> 00:34:35,440
I almost didn't recognize you.

570
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:38,670
There have been

571
00:34:39,240 --> 00:34:40,400
