573
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:43,630
Please forgive me.

574
00:34:44,630 --> 00:34:46,440
Here are some pastries.

575
00:34:47,280 --> 00:34:49,240
Please accept them.

576
00:34:49,240 --> 00:34:50,240
(Moon Resto)

577
00:34:50,240 --> 00:34:52,190
