580
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:57,840
What's the occasion today?

581
00:34:58,110 --> 00:34:59,320
Why are you so generous?

582
00:35:00,590 --> 00:35:03,030
It's because my nephew, Xu Qi'an,

583
00:35:03,320 --> 00:35:05,150
accidentally injured a Silver Gong

584
00:35:05,470 --> 00:35:06,590
and was sentenced to death

585
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:10,070
by Lord Wei.

586
00:35:10,240 --> 00:35:11,990
So, I was hoping

587
00:35:11,990 --> 00:35:13,630
to ask the Vice Minister

588
00:35:14,030 --> 00:35:15,470
to intercede

589
00:35:17,150 --> 00:35:18,280
and save

590
00:35:18,550 --> 00:35:19,880
my nephew's life.

591
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:24,030
My husband
is the Vice Minister of Rites.

592
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:25,960
He does have

593
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:28,440
- influence in the court.
- Yes.

594
00:35:28,670 --> 00:35:31,030
However, with his high position,

595
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:34,920
he can't help a condemned criminal
for no reason.

596
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:37,590
If political rivals get hold of this,

597
00:35:37,800 --> 00:35:39,550
he'd suffer because of me.

598
00:35:41,150 --> 00:35:43,400
You'd better take these back.

599
00:35:44,030 --> 00:35:45,470
Let's go home.

600
00:35:59,380 --> 00:36:06,380
(Xu Residence)

601
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:12,800
Dear.

602
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:16,280
Dear.

603
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:18,510
What did Wang Xiuhe say?

604
00:36:26,150 --> 00:36:27,960
She agreed to help.

605
00:36:32,030 --> 00:36:32,960
Where's your bracelet?

606
00:36:34,280 --> 00:36:35,920
I exchanged it for favors.

607
00:36:35,920 --> 00:36:37,400
That was part of your dowry.

608
00:36:38,240 --> 00:36:40,070
It's just a possession.

609
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:42,630
When Ningyan returns,

610
00:36:43,190 --> 00:36:45,240
I'll deduct it
from his next month's salary.

611
00:36:46,320 --> 00:36:48,670
How did the Bureau respond?

612
00:36:51,510 --> 00:36:52,840
I met Song Qing.

613
00:36:53,720 --> 00:36:54,560
He said

614
00:36:56,070 --> 00:36:57,360
the Bureau couldn't interfere

615
00:36:58,280 --> 00:36:59,840
in Guardians' matters.

616
00:37:02,150 --> 00:37:03,960
The Imperial Guards also...

617
00:37:12,720 --> 00:37:14,630
As his uncle, I've failed.

618
00:37:30,070 --> 00:37:32,800
Now is not the time to despair.

619
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:35,670
Let's wait for Xinnian's return.

620
00:37:36,110 --> 00:37:37,360
Perhaps...

621
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:44,990
Perhaps he has a solution.

622
00:38:01,510 --> 00:38:03,590
I'm just a small Copper Gong.

623
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:06,990
My words are insignificant.

624
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:09,590
I don't have the right to choose.

625
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:14,650
You're paid as a court official.

626
00:38:15,550 --> 00:38:17,030
You live off the people's resources.

627
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:19,490
You can easily oppress
the common people,

628
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:21,130
but you can't fool the heavens.

629
00:38:23,720 --> 00:38:25,440
I meant it too.

630
00:38:33,030 --> 00:38:34,360
The human minds are hard to read.

631
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:36,150
Judging hearts is like solving cases.

632
00:38:36,630 --> 00:38:37,510
One must not

633
00:38:37,630 --> 00:38:39,070
make hasty conclusions

634
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:40,720
based on temporary biases.

635
00:38:46,820 --> 00:38:49,460
(Steadfast Enforcement)

636
00:38:51,670 --> 00:38:53,320
Do you think I judged wrongly?

637
00:38:53,340 --> 00:38:54,740
