I dare not.

638
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:57,440
However, Xu Qi'an only acted
out of righteousness

639
00:38:57,670 --> 00:38:58,990
because the Silver Gong

640
00:38:58,990 --> 00:39:00,470
humiliated a woman.

641
00:39:00,590 --> 00:39:01,550
I believe

642
00:39:01,550 --> 00:39:02,390
this act

643
00:39:02,550 --> 00:39:05,110
serves to deter immorality
within the yamen.

644
00:39:05,440 --> 00:39:07,240
Lord Wei, please have mercy

645
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:09,150
and spare Copper Gong Xu's life.

646
00:39:10,240 --> 00:39:12,440
